          {
            "title": "Intro 2",
            "id": 126992,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Crear una variable para cada uno de tus amigos haría que tu código fuera largo y complejo.</p><code name=\"main.swift\" version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" friend1 = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Tom&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" friend2 = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Mia&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" friend3 = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Lee&quot;\" class=\"string\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"4\" endIndex=\"11\" /><option startIndex=\"24\" endIndex=\"31\" /><option startIndex=\"44\" endIndex=\"51\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>friend1</code> seguido de <code>friend2</code> y finalmente <code>friend3</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Square brackets",
            "id": 126993,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>En lugar de crear una variable para el nombre de cada amigo, podemos agrupar todos los valores en un <strong>array</strong> usando <code>[</code> y <code>]</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" friends = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;Tom&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;Mia&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;Lee&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"]\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(friends)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"14\" endIndex=\"15\" /><option startIndex=\"34\" endIndex=\"35\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"{\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"}\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"[&quot;Tom&quot;, &quot;Mia&quot;, &quot;Lee&quot;]\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>[</code> seguido de <code>]</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Element",
            "id": 126994,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Los valores de un array se llaman <strong>elementos</strong>. Por ejemplo, <code>\"Tom\"</code>, <code>\"Mia\"</code> y <code>\"Lee\"</code> son elementos de este array.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" friends = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;Tom&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;Mia&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;Lee&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"]\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(friends);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"29\" endIndex=\"34\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"3\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"[&quot;Tom&quot;, &quot;Mia&quot;, &quot;Lee&quot;]\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>\"Lee\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Arrays",
            "id": 126995,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para crear un array vacío en Swift, usamos <code>[]</code>, el tipo del array y <code>()</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" friends = [\" /><text value=\"String\" class=\"type\" /><text value=\"]()\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(friends)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"14\" endIndex=\"22\" /><option startIndex=\"22\" endIndex=\"23\" /><option startIndex=\"23\" endIndex=\"24\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"{\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"}\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"[]\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>[String]</code> seguido de <code>(</code> y finalmente <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Value in an array",
            "id": 126996,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Colocar una cadena entre los corchetes crea un array con un valor, pruébalo con <code>\"Tom\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" friends = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;Tom&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"]\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(friends)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"15\" endIndex=\"20\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"[&quot;Tom&quot;]\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>\"Tom\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
